&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant Respiratory Physician&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chelsea &amp; Westminster Hospital NHS Trust invites applications for a substantive post in Respiratory Medicine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is mainly based at our West Middlesex site in Isleworth where the successful candidate will join a team of 4 consultants who provide General Respiratory, Lung Cancer, Sleep and TB services to the local population.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role includes general respiratory and lung cancer clinics, participation in the Lung MDT, inpatient ward work with input to our Enhanced Care Area on the Acute Medical Unit, and support / supervision of our Respiratory junior medical staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Trust encourages and supports all consultants to be involved in education and research and enjoys strong links with local hospitals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sadia Khan - Service Director&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address - sadia.khan@chelwest.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
